quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  18,98,"Naboola mbu: “Tsino ni tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi. Ne olwa yiliula indache ya Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, alishifunakafunaka muno. Ne indache ya Nyasaye wanje Omulesi ni yahabwene.""
  18,99,"Ne khulibalekha abeene khubeene beenjiranemwo, ne olwa olwika lulifurwamwo, awo khulibakhung’asia boosi halala."
  18,100,"Ne khulilolosia Jahanamu inyanga eyo imbeli wabakhayi malolosia."
  18,101,"Abetsimoni tsiabu tsiali tsiafunikhwa ehale nende ametsulilo kefu, ne shibali nibanyala okhuwulila tawe."
  18,102,"Koo, balia abakhaya baparanga mbu banyala okhukhola Abasumba banje abalina babu habundu wanje? Toto efwe khwarecheshela Jahannam abakhayi ibe wabaliishila."
  18,103,"Boola mbu: “Koo, ebabilekhwo balia bebikhole biabu biabiiya muno?”"
  18,104,"Ni balia bobukhalabani bwabu bwakora eshikhaya mubulamu bwokhushialo, nabo baparanga mbu bakholanga ebikhole ebilayi."
  18,105,"Abo nibo bakhaya ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi nende okhubukana ninaye. Kho, ebikhole biabu nibikwa akhaya, ne shikhulibateba inyanga yeyindukho tawe."
  18,106,"Kho, Jahanam nikwo omurungo kwabu shichila bakhaya mana nibakholela omubayo ebimanyisio bianje nende Abarumwa banje."
  18,107,"Toto balia abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, ameshelo kabu kaliba Firdaws."
  18,108,"Balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi, shibalienya okhurulamwo tawe."
  18,109,"Boola mbu: “Inyanza yibetsanga mbu nibwo obwino bwokhuhandika amakhuwa ka Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, inyanza yakhomele amakhuwa ka Nyasaye wanje Omulesi nikashili okhuwa, kata khureranga etsindi shinga etso."
  18,110,"Boola mbu: “Toto esie endisa Omundu shinga enywe, efimbulilungwa mbu Nyasaye wenyu ni Nyasaye mulala. Kho, ulia wikomba okhubukana nende Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, akhole ebikhole ebilayi, ne alatsokaasiakhwo yesiyesi khumalamo ka Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi tawe.""